        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "You may have taken things a bit too far.\n\nBetween the foster homes you grew up in and the rough streets you roamed on, you had to always be making a play just to survive. It wasn't as if you were little and said \"I want to be a con-artist\" when I grow up, but it was how you got by. If there is a scam out there, you've run it, and you were pretty good at it too. Good enough to not get caught, at least. For a while there, when the whole \"ghost hunter\" craze took off, you ran one where you were a \"para-psychologist\" who would get in touch with the ghosts of the dead and comfort grieving family members about it. That sort of blew up into hunting the dead in old houses with people who thought this stuff was real. You sold your services, you made a pretty penny. And then the Tremere came calling, curious about your abilities. Your own story may have gotten away from you a bit, because they decided you'd be a perfect person to embrace.\n\nWell, the joke is on you now! You weren't able to see ghosts before and now, you are haunted by them, which is both creepy and annoying, especially as you don't even know what to do about it. Worse, you are now fighting to survive in a clan full of weird, vampire/magey/doomseday survivialists who thought you were some sort of medium and you weren't - at least you weren't then. Before your Embrace, you didn't have an announce of magic in you for real. Now, you have learned quickly, picking up Thaumaturgy and the occult, if nothing else just to keep your head above water. Besides, it could prove to be useful, right? Maybe you can figure out a way to parlay that into something, right, especially with all the dark things you hear whispered about.\n\nWhat you hadn't banked on was that this clan was so big on rank and file, and you've been transferred out of Five Burroughs Chantry in New York to Los Angeles Chantry. You've arrived here without a clue to the situation, outside of a report saying something about demons and some ritual some Lord cast and that apparently there is angels there, crazy shit. You have a couple of buddies out here, at least, friends from the con games of old, and some influences from your days running scams. You aren't completely uprooted and destitute on this cost. But, the deeper you get into this Tremere, vampire crazy, the harder it is to swim. You just need to keep spinning all your plates!"
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Sire:",
          "column_2": "Felix Epstein",
          "column_3": "Reference: (If any)",
          "column_4": "New York by Night",
          "column_6": "Clan",
          "column_7": "Tremere - Easily Bound"
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Embrace Date:",
          "column_2": 2010,
          "column_3": "Embrace Location:",
          "column_4": "Newark, NJ",
          "column_6": "Generation",
          "column_7": "Neonate 11"
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Who You Know",
          "column_2": "Your relationship to these people is described. This may mean they do not know you."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Starting Goals",
          "column_2": "These are recomendations, not mandates."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "You are thrown into this crazy world, but you can't let them know you are in over your head. Convince everyone you know exactly what you are talking about (most of it, you don't)."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Find someone to be useful for. Always have a fall back person to rely on if everything hits the fan. Find someone to be a patron to protect you when and if you need it."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Prestation is the currency of this societies economy. Start collecting it, scamming for it, or bartering for it to ensure you have enough valuable boons to keep you safe if you need or to convert to something more valuable if want."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "You are now REALLY haunted by ghosts (cause of course, payback for you being a smart ass). Find someone, anyone to help you get rid of these, because frankly, it's creepy and annoying."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Player Amended History",
          "column_3": "Date Submited"
        }
      ]
    },
